This did not solve the problem. Although my tests at desktop passed 20x without problems, there were failures exposed here. Will need further investigation.

Well, one very bad thing that I did in my change was to cancel before shutting down multiple threads on the sync client. The problem here was that it would race with the possible refreshing of the stream in the case of capped streams. I'm dropping that commit and rebasing.
